attributes.mlflow.spanInputs: {"prompt": "Generate telemetry model-driven configuration for OSPF protocol on IOS XR. Server: 10.20.20.10, port: 57400, protocol: tcp, encoding: self-describing-gpb."}
attributes.mlflow.spanOutputs:
"telemetry model-driven
 sensor-group OSPF-INFO
  sensor-path Cisco-IOS-XR-infra-xtc-agent-oper:xtc/topology-nodes/topology-node/ipv4-link/remote-node-protocol-identifier/igp-information/igp/ospf
 !
 destination-group DG-GRPC
  address-family ipv4
   destination 10.20.20.10
    port 57400
    encoding self-describing-gpb
    protocol grpc no-tls
 !
 subscription SUB-OSPF
  sensor-group-id OSPF-INFO sample-interval 30000
  destination-group-id DG-GRPC
 !"
